OL,5,G2000 The Myth Of Marilyn Monroe
OL,6,     FMarilyn Monroe is the defining
OL,7,     Ficon of the 50s. A shining example
OL,8,     Fof the American dream. However, as
OL,9,     Fthe decade continued, the myth of
OL,10,     FMarilyn and the American Dream
OL,11,     Fseemed to crumble.
OL,12,G2100 I Am Raquel Welch
OL,13,     FCelebrating the life of a
OL,14,     Ftrailblazing actress and single
OL,15,     Fmother who not only redefined the
OL,16,     Fworld's idea of a Hollywood sex
OL,17,     Fsymbol, but also led the way for
OL,18,     Fmodern-day action heroines.
